data.description: Spacious 4 BR, 3 BA home on Cul-De-sac with huge 3 tiered back yard.  Relax in the back yard oasis with large covered patio overlooking nice landscape which includes a waterfall and fire pit. The main level features the kitchen with all the stainless steel appliances.  There is a formal dining room, family room with access to the back patio, living room, a master onsuite and an additional bedroom and bathroom, laundry room with washer/dryer/freezer and double attached garage. The lower level is finished with 2 more bedrooms, ¾ bath and huge rec room area with pool table and a small kitchen. Other features include recently installed roof solar panels (with tax credit available) central air and radon system. Walking distance to belmar park and shopping center.
